---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section id="hero" class="relative w-full h-screen overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Breathing Circles -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10">
    <div class="breathing-circle circle-1"></div>
    <div class="breathing-circle circle-2"></div>
    <div class="breathing-circle circle-3"></div>
    <div class="breathing-circle circle-4"></div>
    <div class="breathing-circle circle-5"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Background for Desktop (Spline) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 hidden lg:block" style="transform: scale(0.5) translateX(45%) translateY(-40%);";">
    <spline-viewer loading-anim-type="spinner-small-dark" url="https://prod.spline.design/ANgSimz09kRzUctd/scene.splinecode"></spline-viewer>
  </div>

  <!-- Text Content -->
  <div class="relative z-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:items-start h-full">
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left px-6 lg:px-0 lg:pl-24">
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light">Hola, soy</p>
      <h1 class="animated-gradient-text text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold my-2">
        Arantxa
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        Una apasionada desarrolladora web con experiencia en la creación de experiencias digitales modernas y atractivas. Me especializo en el desarrollo front-end y me encanta dar vida a las ideas a través del código.
      </p>

      <!-- Profile Picture for Mobile/Tablet -->
      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center lg:hidden">
          <img src="/arantxa-photo.png" alt="Foto de Arantxa" class="rounded-full w-32 h-32 object-cover border-4 border-primary shadow-lg">
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  @import '../styles/hero.css';
</style>

<script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/@splinetool/viewer@1.10.87/build/spline-viewer.js" async></script>